          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Apply the trailing RTO rate to orders despatched but not yet delivered at the cut off date. If Rs 40 lakh of orders are in transit on 31 March and the trailing RTO rate is 18 percent, provide Rs 7.2 lakh by reversing revenue and reinstating the inventory at cost rather than at selling price, plus the forward and return freight."
